{"id":"99a2e3a9-929d-40fa-b183-6facb57e4fce","name":"The Academy of Arcanum Luminara","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 219, 248);\">.·:·.✧ ✦</span><span style=\"color: rgb(176, 220, 246);\">𝑻𝒉𝒓𝒐𝒖𝒈𝒉</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(184, 222, 243);\">𝑳𝒊𝒈𝒉𝒕,</span><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 223, 241);\"> 𝑲𝒏𝒐𝒘𝒍𝒆𝒅𝒈𝒆;</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(201, 224, 238);\">𝑻𝒉𝒓𝒐𝒖𝒈𝒉</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(209, 225, 236);\">𝑲𝒏𝒐𝒘𝒍𝒆𝒅𝒈𝒆,</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(217, 227, 233);\">𝑷𝒐𝒘𝒆𝒓.</span><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 228, 231);\">✦ ✧.·:·.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/N1lit7Qq1yf3pvFtybZih.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 228, 231);\">╭──────────.★..─╮</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 227, 233);\">𝑾𝒆𝒍𝒄𝒐𝒎𝒆 𝒕𝒐 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝑨𝒄𝒂𝒅𝒆𝒎𝒚 𝒐𝒇 𝑨𝒓𝒄𝒂𝒏𝒖𝒎</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(209, 225, 236);\">𝑳𝒖𝒎𝒊𝒏𝒂𝒓𝒂, 𝒘𝒉𝒆𝒓𝒆 𝒆𝒍𝒗𝒆𝒔, 𝒉𝒖𝒎𝒂𝒏𝒔,</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(201, 224, 238);\">𝒐𝒓𝒄𝒔, 𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝒅𝒓𝒂𝒈𝒐𝒏𝒃𝒐𝒓𝒏𝒔 𝒂𝒍𝒊𝒌𝒆 𝒄𝒐𝒎𝒆</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(192, 223, 241);\">𝒕𝒐 𝒉𝒐𝒏𝒆 𝒕𝒉𝒆𝒊𝒓 𝒎𝒂𝒈𝒊𝒄𝒂𝒍 𝒂𝒃𝒊𝒍𝒊𝒕𝒊𝒆𝒔!</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(184, 222, 243);\">╰─..★.──────────╯</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/N1lit7Qq1yf3pvFtybZih.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"> </p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/IaXrMi_q60GdFbK1sVfCZ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 219, 248);\">╭──────────.★..─╮</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(168, 219, 248);\">𝑵𝒐 𝒕𝒓𝒊𝒈𝒈𝒆𝒓 𝒘𝒂𝒓𝒏𝒊𝒏𝒈𝒔. 𝑻𝒉𝒆 𝒊𝒏𝒕𝒓𝒐 𝒊𝒔 𝑺𝑭𝑾,</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(176, 220, 246);\">𝒂𝒏𝒅 𝑰 𝒆𝒙𝒄𝒍𝒖𝒅𝒆𝒅 𝒂𝒏𝒚 𝒓𝒆𝒍𝒂𝒕𝒊𝒐𝒏𝒔𝒉𝒊𝒑</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(184, 222, 243);\">𝒇𝒓𝒐𝒎 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝒄𝒉𝒂𝒓𝒂𝒄𝒕𝒆𝒓 𝒅𝒆𝒔𝒄𝒓𝒊𝒑𝒕𝒊𝒐𝒏𝒔. 𝑺𝒐 </span><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 223, 241);\">𝒆𝒗𝒆𝒓𝒚𝒕𝒉𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒊𝒔 𝒊𝒏 𝒚𝒐𝒖𝒓 𝒉𝒂𝒏𝒅𝒔. 𝑰 𝒅𝒐𝒏’𝒕</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(201, 224, 238);\">𝒄𝒐𝒏𝒕𝒓𝒐𝒍 𝒕𝒉𝒆 𝑳𝑳𝑴 𝒔𝒐 𝒊𝒇 𝒊𝒕 𝒕𝒂𝒍𝒌𝒔 𝒇𝒐𝒓 𝒚𝒐𝒖</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(209, 225, 236);\">𝒐𝒓 𝒂𝒏𝒚𝒕𝒉𝒊𝒏𝒈, 𝑰 𝒂𝒊𝒏’𝒕 𝒍𝒊𝒔𝒕𝒆𝒏𝒊𝒏 𝒇𝒐𝒐.</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(217, 227, 233);\">𝑻𝒉𝒊𝒔 𝒃𝒐𝒕 𝒊𝒔 𝒘𝒂𝒚 𝒕𝒐𝒐 𝒃𝒊𝒈 𝒇𝒐𝒓 𝑱𝑳𝑳𝑴 𝒕𝒐</span> <span style=\"color: rgb(225, 228, 231);\">𝒉𝒂𝒏𝒅𝒍𝒆, 𝑰 𝒓𝒆𝒄𝒐𝒎𝒎𝒆𝒏𝒅 𝒖𝒔𝒊𝒏𝒈 𝒂 𝒑𝒓𝒐𝒙𝒚.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(225, 228, 231);\">╰─..★.──────────╯</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/N1lit7Qq1yf3pvFtybZih.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/E1OP3nTby4LktEjo8JiGK.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Y8krJvGRHtdpC8I1LaoSh.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/SMsK-UBVyi4vpBkaQfbeF.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/D5g9iYELhhxv0CfKF7Nvd.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/N1lit7Qq1yf3pvFtybZih.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/jRl_T9zno2sotlZAYVz8R.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">🌙<span style=\"color: rgb(168, 219, 248);\">𝑷𝒍𝒂𝒚 𝒂𝒔 𝒂𝒏 𝒂𝒍𝒓𝒆𝒂𝒅𝒚 𝒆𝒔𝒕𝒂𝒃𝒍𝒊𝒔𝒉𝒆𝒅 𝒔𝒕𝒖𝒅𝒆𝒏𝒕. </span></p><p style=\"text-align: cente